

### Grammy?



### Perini

* 2 cups buttermilk
* 2 eggs
* 1 t baking soda
* 2 C yellow cornmeal
1 t salt
* 3-4 T melted butter
* drop of vanilla
* 2 T sugar (optional)

* combine buttermlik, eggs, baking soda and beat well
* in a separate bowl, combine cornmeal, salt
* add buttermilk mixture, butter, vanilla and mix well
* pour into a greased cast-iron skillet
* bake at 450 until golden brown

